Preheat oven to 325 degrees F. In large bowl, with mixer, beat egg yolks and EAGLE BRAND(r) until well blended. Stir in lemon juice. Pour into crust. Bake 30 minutes. In saucepan, combine raspberries and cornstarch; cook and stir until mixture thickens and is clear. Spoon on top of pie. Chill at least 4 hours. Top with whipped topping. Garnish as desired. Store leftovers covered in refrigerator.